none.description:
{Fortune}

Increases Luck of target allied unit by +1.

While Fortune lasts, Luck penalties cannot reduce that unit below +1 Luck.

basic.description:
{Basic Fortune}

Increases Luck of target allied unit by +1.

While Fortune lasts, Luck penalties cannot reduce that unit below +1 Luck.

advanced.description:
{Advanced Fortune}

Increases Luck of target allied unit by +2.

While Fortune lasts, Luck penalties cannot reduce that unit below +2 Luck.

expert.description:
{Expert Fortune}

Increases Luck of all allied units by +2.

While Fortune lasts, Luck penalties cannot reduce affected units below +2 Luck.
